name: Blue-eyes White Dragon
description:
An extremely rare   

card with

unsurpassed attack

and defense power.

name: Mystical Elf
description:
A delicate elf that 

lacks in offense

but has a terrific

defense backed by

mystical power.

name: Hitotsu-me Giant
description:
A one-eyed behemoth 

with thick, powerful

arms made for

delivering punishing

blows.

name: Baby Dragon
description:
Much more than just 

a child, this dragon

is gifted with

untapped power.

name: Ryu-kishin
description:
A very elusive 

creature that looks 

like a harmless

statue until it

attacks.

name: Feral Imp
description:
A playful little 

imp that lurks in 

the dark, waiting to

attack an unwary

enemy.

name: Winged Dragon #1
description:
A dragon commonly 

found guarding 

mountain fortresses.

Its signature attack

is a sweeping dive 

from out of the blue.

name: Mushroom Man
description:
Found in moist

areas, this monster 

launches poison

spores against its

enemies.

name: Shadow Specter
description:
Ghostly beast that 

appears in the

wasteland and is

particularly

troublesome when

faced in large

numbers.

name: Blackland Fire Dragon
description:
A dragon that dwells

in the depths of

darkness. Its

defensive capability

suffers from its

poor eyesight.

name: Sword Arm of Dragon
description:
With a body covered 

in sword-like

thorns, nothing

dares stand in the

way of this monster 

when it charges.

name: Swamp Battleguard
description:
This creature is    

armed with a spiked 

club that can

destroy almost

anything in its path.

Rumored to have a

brother that is just

as destructive.

name: Tyhone
description:
Capable of firing

cannonballs from its

mouth for long-range

attacks against

enemies.

name: Battle Steer
description:
A bull monster often

found in the woods.

Charges enemy

monsters with a pair

of razor-sharp horns.

name: Flame Swordsman
description:
A fighter gifted

with the power of

fire.

Attacks enemies with

a sword that

launches flames.

name: Time Wizard
description:
A sorcerer capable

of bending time to

his will. Though not

powerful at first

glance, appearances 

can be deceiving.

name: Right Leg of the Forbidden One
description:
A forbidden limb

sealed by magic.

Whoever breaks

this seal will know

infinite power.

Only one card of

this type may be

included in a deck.

name: Left Leg of the Forbidden One
description:
A forbidden limb

sealed by magic.

Whoever breaks

this seal will know

infinite power.

Only one card of

this type may be

included in a deck.

name: Right Arm of the Forbidden One
description:
A forbidden limb

sealed by magic.

Whoever breaks

this seal will know

infinite power.

Only one card of

this type may be

included in a deck.

name: Left Arm of the Forbidden One
description:
A forbidden limb

sealed by magic.

Whoever breaks

this seal will know

infinite power.

Only one card of

this type may be

included in a deck.

name: Exodia the Forbidden
description:
Once combined with

arms and legs, this 

monster is freed

from its magical

chains.

Only one card of

this type may be

included in a deck.

name: Summoned Skull
description:
An entity with dark

powers for confusing

the enemy. Among the

FIEND class of

monsters, this is a 

pretty rare card.

name: The Wicked Worm Beast
description:
A monster worm

created by the

powers of darkness. 

It suddenly appears 

from under the

ground to attack its

enemies.

name: Skull Servant
description:
A skeletal ghost

that isn't strong

but can mean trouble

in large numbers.

name: Horn Imp
description:
A small imp that

dwells in the dark.

Its single horn

makes it a

formidable opponent.

name: Battle Ox
description:
A monster with

tremendous power.

Destroys enemies

with a swing of its

axe.

name: Beaver Warrior
description:
What this creature 

lacks in size,

it makes up for

in defense when

battling in the

meadow.

name: Rock Ogre Grotto #1
description:
Protected by a solid

body of rock, this

creature throws

a bone-shattering

punch.

name: Mountain Warrior
description:
A solid warrior that

can move swiftly

over rough terrain.

name: Zombie Warrior
description:
A deceptively

fragile-looking

skeleton warrior

that is known for

its swift and

precise attacks.

name: Koumori Dragon
description:
A vicious,

fire-breathing

dragon whose wicked

flames corrupt the

souls of its victims.

name: Two-headed King Rex
description:
An unusual and

rarely seen

two-headed dragon.

name: Judge Man
description:
For this

club-wielding

warrior, there is

no other outcome

to battle than

victory or defeat.

name: Saggi the Dark Clown
description:
This clown appears 

out of nowhere and 

executes some very 

strange moves to 

avoid enemy attacks.

name: Dark Magician
description:
The ultimate wizard 

in terms of attack

and defense.

name: The Snake Hair
description:
A monster with the

head of a poisonus

snake. One look will

turn an unwary

opponent to stone.

name: Gaia the Dragon Champion
description:
A warrior's prowess 

combines with a

dragon's speed to

create a powerful

offensive force.

name: Gaia the Fierce Knight
description:
A knight mounted on 

a horse that travels

faster than the wind.

His battle charge is

a force to be

reckoned with.

name: Curse of Dragon
description:
A wicked dragon that

taps dark forces to 

execute a powerful

attack.

name: Dragon Piper
description:
A jar carved with

strange patterns. It

has a particularly

high defense factor.

name: Celtic Guardian
description:
An elf, who learned

to wield a sword,

baffles enemies with

lightning-swift

attacks.

name: Illusionist Faceless Mage
description:
Manipulates enemy

attacks with the

power of illusion.

A very rare card.

name: Karbonala Warrior
description:
A very

average-looking

fighter with an

unusually high

attack factor.

name: Rogue Doll
description:
A unique doll gifted

with mystical power.

Particularly

powerful when

attacking against

dark forces.

name: Oscillo Hero #2
description:
Attacks its enemies

with thunder.

name: Griffore
description:
This creature's

tough hide deflects

just about any

attack.

name: Torike
description:
Not as tough as it

looks in terms of

defense.

This monster's

sharp horn gives it

an edge

when attacking.

name: Sangan
description:
A compact,

three-eyed monster

that is dangerous

when faced

in the dark.

name: Big Insect
description:
A giant ant that

dwells in the jungle.

Powerful in terms of

both ATK and DEF

factors.

name: Basic Insect
description:
Usually found

travelling in swarms,

this creature's

ideal environment is

the forest.

name: Armored Lizard
description:
A lizard with a very

tough hide and a

very vicious bite.

name: Hercules Beetle
description:
A massive beetle

with a tough hide

and a dangerous horn.

name: Killer Needle
description:
A huge bee with

exceptional strength.

Particularly

dangerous when a

swarm is encountered.

name: Gokibore
description:
A large, spherical

roach that attacks

its enemies by

rolling over them.

Its tough defense

makes it 

a formidable foe.

name: Giant Flea
description:
A giant

blood-sucking flea

that's devastating

when attacking.

name: Larvae Moth
description:
Not much in its

larval form,

this creature is a

force to be reckoned

with when it grows

to become a colossal

moth.

name: Great Moth
description:
A powerful creature

of the forest, this

huge moth attacks

its enemies by

spreading poison

dust with its wings.

name: Kuriboh
description:
By itself, this

small creature may

not seem like much.

But in the dark, it

attacks in numbers

as a formidable

force.

name: Mammoth Graveyard
description:
A mammoth that

protects the

gravesite of its

pack. It's

absolutely merciless

when facing

graverobbers.

name: Great White
description:
A giant white shark

with razor-sharp

teeth.

name: Wolf
description:
A rarely seen wolf

with a powerful nose

for catching the

scent of an enemy.

name: Harpie Lady
description:
A human-shaped

animal with wings.

Beautiful to watch,

but lethal when

engaged in battle.

name: Harpie Lady Sisters
description:
Three fierce sisters

who relentlessly

attack as a team.

name: Tiger Axe
description:
A fast and powerful

axe-wielding

beast warrior.

name: Silver Fang
description:
A snow wolf that's

beautiful to the eye

but absolutely

vicious in battle.

name: Kojikocy
description:
A man-hunter with

powerful arms that

can crush boulders.

name: Perfectly Ultimate Great Moth
description:
The final

incarnation of the

ultimate insect,

the Great Moth!

name: Garoozis
description:
An axe-swinging

beast warrior with

the head of

a dragon.

name: Thousand Dragon
description:
A dragon that has

grown and developed

over a thousand

years.

name: Fiend Kraken
description:
A massive squid that

suddenly appears

from the depths of

the sea to attack

unwary enemies.

name: Jellyfish
description:
An almost invisible,

semi-transparent

jellyfish that

drifts in the sea.

name: Cocoon of Evolution
description:
This creature is

capable of instantly

evolving larvae

into adults.

name: Kairyu-shin
description:
A sea dragon that's

referred to as the

"King of the Ocean".

It attacks its

enemies with huge

tidal waves.

name: Giant Soldier of Stone
description:
A giant warrior made

of stone. A punch

from this creature

has earth-shaking

results.

name: Man-eating Plant
description:
A meat-eating plant

that is attractive

to the eye but

dangerous when

approached.

name: Krokodilus
description:
A vicious crocodile

with intelligence.

Hard scales form

a natural armor

for this creature.

name: Grappler
description:
A devious snake with

a thick body that

wraps around an

enemy monster and

squeezes the life

out of it.

name: Axe Raider
description:
An axe-wielding

monster of

tremendous strength

and agility.

name: Megazowler
description:
Nothing stands in

the way of this

spike-covered

dinosaur.

name: Uraby
description:
Fast on its feet,

this dinosaur rips

enemies to shreds

with its sharp claws.

name: Crawling Dragon #2
description:
A powerful dragon

with teeth that can

grind almost

anything to dust.

name: Red-eyes B. Dragon
description:
A very rare card

with a high-level

ATK factor.

name: Castle of Dark Illusions
description:
A creature that can

generate darkness to

envelop all that

exists around it.

name: Reaper of the Cards
description:
This monster boasts

a strong defense and

a massive scythe

that cuts through

almost anything.

name: King of Yamimakai
description:
Wields the power of

darkness to destroy

its enemies.

name: Barox
description:
This creature flies

through the dark,

attacking its

enemies with its

long, hairy arms.

name: Dark Chimera
description:
A fire-breathing

monster that dwells

in the netherworld.

name: Metal Guardian
description:
A fiend guarding

the treasures of

the netherworld.

Its defense is

particularly high in

 a dark environment.

name: Catapult Turtle
description:
Well-protected by

its shell, this

monster flings

projectiles from

its catapult.

name: Gyakutenno Megami
description:
Uses her mystical

power to protect the

weak and provide

spiritual support.

name: Mystic Horseman
description:
Half man and half

horse, this monster

is known for its

extreme speed.

name: Rabid Horseman
description:
A powerful

and unstoppable

combination of

bull and horse.

name: Zanki
description:
Prefers to face

enemies one-on-one.

His swiftly drawn

blade delivers a

quick and immediate

finnish.

name: Crawling Dragon
description:
A weakened dragon

that can no longer

fly, but is still a

formidable force

to be reckoned with.

name: Crass Clown
description:
A performer

in the Dark Circus,

this clown drains

the strength of

its enemies with

strange dances.

name: Armored Zombie
description:
A warrior raised

from the beyond.

Blindly swings

a sharp blade with

devastating force.

name: Dragon Zombie
description:
A dragon revived by

sorcery. Its breath

is highly corrosive.

name: Clown Zombie
description:
A clown revived by

the powers of

darkness.

Its strange dance

has sent many 

monsters to their

ends.

name: Pumpking the King of Ghosts
description:
This pumpkin king

strikes at its

enemies with its

long tentacles.

name: Battle Warrior
description:
A warrior that

fights with his

bare hands.

name: Wings of Wicked Flame
description:
Soaring over

its enemies on wings

of crimson fire,

this monster attacks

by blasting flames

from its body.

name: Mask of Darkness
description:
A shadow mask

created by the hands

of a dark mage.

name: Job-change Mirror
description:
An indestructible,

wicked mirror that

blocks enemy attacks.

name: Curtain of the Dark Ones
description:
A curtain woven by

the hands of a

sorcerer. It is said

to enhance the power

of magic- users.

name: Tomozaurus
description:
A deceivingly small

creature that is so

vicious it attacks

both friend and foe

without discretion.

name: Spirit of the Winds
description:
A spirit of the wind

that freely sails

the skies. Known to

generate storms when

it's in a bad mood.

name: Kageningen
description:
Uses both its

physical and shadow

forms to attack,

making it

a difficult creature

to overcome.

name: Graveyard and the Hand of Invitation
description:
A final resting

place that enhances

the power of the

doomed and drains

that of the living.

name: Goddess with the Third Eye
description:
A goddess with an

all-seeing eye that

reveals all.

name: Hero of the East
description:
A samurai from the

Far East armed with

a razor-sharp sword.

name: Doma The Angel of Silence
description:
This angel rules

over the doomed

and administers it

when necessary.

name: That Which Feeds on Life
description:
A vile monster that

fuels its power by

draining the essence

of life from

its opponents.

name: Dark Gray
description:
Entirely gray,

this beast has

rarely been seen

by mortal eyes.

name: White Magical Hat
description:
A gentleman thief

that eludes the law

despite the fact

that he sticks out

like a sore thumb

with his silk hat

and white cape.

name: Kamion Wizard
description:
A magic-user that

controls chaos

and wields

a mighty sickle.

name: Nightmare Scorpion
description:
A very toxic

creature that

induces nightmares

and attacks its

victims with four

poison- tipped

stingers.

name: Spirit of the Books
description:
A spirit of the

books with infinite

knowledge and

an endless variety

of attack strategies.

name: Supporter in the Shadows
description:
A cute elf that

assists against

enemies while

remaining hidden

from sight.

name: Trial of Nightmares
description:
Passes judgment on

enemies that are

locked in coffins.

name: Dream Clown
description:
The mysterious dance

of this creature

draws its enemies

into eternal slumber.

name: Sleeping Lion
description:
Frequently

found sleeping,

this monster is

very dangerous

when awakened.

name: Yamatano Dragon Scroll
description:
This dragon is

conjured from

a picture scroll

to attack enemies.

It has a pretty

low defense factor.

name: Dark Plant
description:
A vicious flower

raised from polluted

soil and fertilized

by dark forces.

name: Ancient Tool
description:
An engine

of destruction

discovered in the

ruins of an ancient

civilization.

name: Faith Bird
description:
A bird with a very

long tail that

attacks with a light

that emanates from

its entire being.

name: Orion the Battle King
description:
A mysterious

creature known as

the king of warriors,

but nobody has lived

long enough to tell

how it earned

its reputation.

name: Ansatsu
description:
A silent and swift

warrior specializing

in sneak attack.

name: LaMoon
description:
A sorcerer who lives

on the moon and

attacks opponents

with the power

of lunar light.

name: Nemuriko
description:
A child-like

creature that

controls a sleep

spirit to beckon

enemies into eternal

slumber.

name: Weather Control
description:
This monster is

capable of

manipulating the

weather. This power

is the reason behind

the changing climate

of mountains.

name: Octoberser
description:
A strange creature

with the head

of a fish and

the tentacles of

an octopus that

attacks its enemies

with spears.

name: The 13th Grave
description:
A zombie that

suddenly appeared

from plot

#13 - supposedly

an empty grave.

name: Charubin the Fire Knight
description:
A warrior protected

by a shell

that can even

deflect the heat

of burning flames.

name: Mystical Capture Chain
description:
A mystical chain

that is believed

capable of binding

its enemies and

preventing their

attacks.

name: Fiend's Hand
description:
Long arms reach out

from the Swamp

of Chaos to drag

in enemy creatures.

name: Witty Phantom
description:
Dressed in a

night-black tuxedo,

this creature

presides over

the doomed.

name: Mystery Hand
description:
Twisting the fabric

of reality, arms

stretch out from

another dimension

to attack opponents.

name: Dragon Statue
description:
A granite warrior

with a dragon's soul

wields a powerful

sword against

all enemies.

name: Blue-eyed Silver Zombie
description:
A creature rumored

to turn enemies

into zombies

with a strange ray

that emanates

from its eyes.

name: Toad Master
description:
Thousands of years

old, this frog

wizard attacks

enemies with an

army of tadpoles.

name: Spiked Snail
description:
Evolving from the

powers of darkness,

this snail has arms

and legs that allow

swift attacks

against its enemies.

name: Flame Manipulator
description:
Attacks enemies with

fire-related spells,

such as the

"Sea of Flames"

and the

"Wall of Fire".

name: Necrolancer the Timelord
description:
The first in a line

of golems that

appears almost

anywhere from within

a dimensional ring.

name: Djinn the Watcher of the Wind
description:
Controls the air

currents to create

violent winds and

tornadoes to blow

away its enemies.

name: The Bewitching Phantom Thief
description:
A flashy,

black-caped thief

who wields

a magic cane.

name: Temple of Skulls
description:
A weird temple

of skulls and bones

that sucks the

living essence

of all those who

dare approach it.

name: Monster Egg
description:
A warrior hidden

within an egg that

attacks enemies by

flinging eggshells.

name: The Shadow Who Controls the Dark
description:
A living shadow

that dwells in the

realm of darkness.

It paralyzes

its enemies

to prevent attacks.

name: Lord of the Lamp
description:
A giant that appears

from a mystic lamp

and follows

the orders

of the lamp's owner.

name: Akihiron
description:
A mysterious

creature that dwells

below the sea.

name: Rhaimundos of the Red Sword
description:
A warrior armed

with the Sword

of Crimson Flames.

Uses fire to bind

the movement

of its enemies.

name: The Melting Red Shadow
description:
A creature that

melts into the earth,

melds with an

opponent's shadow,

and attacks

from below.

name: Dokuroizo the Grim Reaper
description:
A living spirit that

preys on the living

essence of enemies.

name: Fire Reaper
description:
A creature that

deals out punishment

with its

flaming arrows.

name: Larvas
description:
A fast-moving,

bird-like creature

that strangles an

opposing monster

with its long,

thin arms.

name: Hard Armor
description:
A living suit of

armor that attacks

enemies with a

bone-jarring tackle.

name: Firegrass
description:
A fire-breathing

plant found growing

near volcanoes.

name: Man Eater
description:
Man-eating plant

with poison feelers

for attacking

enemies.

name: Dig Beak
description:
Coiling its

serpent-like body,

this creature spins

and attacks with

its snapping beak.

name: M-warrior #1
description:
Specializing in

combination attacks,

this warrior uses

magnetism to block

an enemy's escape.

name: M-warrior #2
description:
Specializing in

combination attacks,

this warrior is

equipped with a

tough, magnetically

coated armor.

name: Tainted Wisdom
description:
A parasite brain

that preys

on the knowledge

and intelligence

of its opponents.

name: Lisark
description:
An unusual creature

with sapphire eyes

that creates visions

to confuse the enemy.

name: Lord of Zemia
description:
A vile entity that

deceives enemies

into walking a path

of destruction.

name: The Judgement Hand
description:
The hand of final

judgment is capable

of intense attacks

against the enemy.

name: Mysterious Puppeteer
description:
A puppet master that

manipulates enemies

during battle.

name: Ancient Jar
description:
A fragile jar from

the past containing

a mysterious

creature.

name: Darkfire Dragon
description:
Scorching flames

that wipe out

enemies in the blink

of an eye.

name: Dark King of the Abyss
description:
King of the

netherworld. It's

said that he once

had the power to

rule over the Dark.

name: Spirit of the Harp
description:
A spirit that

soothes the soul

with the music of

its glorious harp.

name: Big Eye
description:
This creature is

covered with

hypnotic eyes

for mesmerizing

its enemies.

name: Armaill
description:
A strange warrior

who manipulates

three fearsome

blades with

both hands and

its tail.

name: Dark Prisoner
description:
This creature

manipulates light

to eliminate

all traces of

its appearance.

name: Hurricail
description:
A twister

that runs rampant

in the wastelands,

cutting its enemies

with blades of wind.

name: Ancient Brain
description:
Exiled from reality,

this creature is

adept at fighting

in the dark.

name: Fire Eye
description:
A winged eye

enveloped in flames

that attacks enemies

with fire.

name: Monsturtle
description:
A vicious turtle

with a spiked shell.

name: Claw Reacher
description:
Stretching arms and

razor-sharp claws

make this monster a

formidable opponent.

name: Phantom Dewan
description:
A wizard

that freezes an

enemy's movement 

with a single curse.

name: Arlownay
description:
A maiden

in the flower

blossoms spreads

poisonous pollen

against opponents.

name: Dark Shade
description:
Emits a dazzling

light from its

crystal to blind

its enemies.

name: Masked Clown
description:
A dancing warrior

that makes mincemeat

out of opponents

with a sharp scythe.

name: Lucky Trinket
description:
A thin and reedy

creature protected

by sacred power.

name: Genin
description:
Uses amazing

sleight-of-hand

to fool and destroy

its enemies.

name: Eyearmor
description:
This warrior

confuses and

destroys enemies

by adopting

their images.

name: Fiend Refrection #2
description:
A bird-beast

that summons

reinforcements

with a hand mirror.

name: Gate Deeg
description:
A creature

with an abdominal

portal used for

summoning monsters

from the netherworld.

name: Synchar
description:
An ugly creature

with two heads and a

mouth for blasting

laser beams.

name: Fusionist
description:
A monstrous cat with

wings and a long,

striking tail.

name: Akakieisu
description:
A wizard

whose incantations

numb the senses of

opposing monsters.

name: LaLa Li-oon
description:
Protected by thunder,

this dangerous cloud

attacks its enemies

with acid rain.

name: Key Mace
description:
A small angel

whose cuteness

melts the hearts

of its enemies.

name: Turtle Tiger
description:
A tiger encased in a

protective shell

that attacks its

enemies with its

razor-sharp fangs.

name: Terra the Terrible
description:
Know as a dweller

of the swamps,

this creature is a

minion of the Dark

forces.

name: Doron
description:
An unpredictable

creature that splits

into two and attacks

an enemy from

opposite directions.

name: Arma Knight
description:
An ammonite warrior

that has protected

the seas from the

dawn of time.

name: Mech Mole Zombie
description:
A creature of the

night that attacks

enemies with its 

rocket-powered arms.

name: Happy Lover
description:
A little angel

that fires beams

of happiness

from the heart jewel

on its forehead.

name: Penguin Knight
description:
A penguin-like

creature that slides

on its belly

to deliver a blow

with its

outstretched sword.

name: Petit Dragon
description:
A very small dragon

known for its

vicious attacks.

name: Frenzied Panda
description:
A savage beast

that carries

a big bamboo stick

for beating down

its enemies.

name: Air Marmot of Nefariousness
description:
A horned beaver

with wings that

throws high-velocity

acorns from the

sky with uncanny

accuracy.

name: Phantom Ghost
description:
Malicious spirits

that walk the world

of the living,

unable to find their

final resting place.

name: Mabarrel
description:
A cannon-like

monster that rapidly

fires eyeballs

at the enemy.

name: Dorover
description:
An ugly, melting

creature that

breathes out

poison gas.

name: Twin Long Rods #1
description:
This creature swings

its whip-like arms

for mid-range

attacks against

enemies.

name: Droll Bird
description:
With a battle cry

that curdles

the blood of

its opponent,

this creature

attacks with its

massive beak.

name: Petit Angel
description:
A quick-moving and

tiny angel that's

very difficult

to hit.

name: Winged Cleaver
description:
This creature

attacks by swinging

around its

sickle-like arms.

name: Hinotama Soul
description:
An intensely hot

flame creature that

rams anything that

stands in its way.

name: Kaminarikozou
description:
This creature stores

lightning within its

body to deliver

electrifying attacks.

name: Meotoko
description:
A huge monster with

a single eye that

fires an intence

beam.

name: Aqua Madoor
description:
A wizard of the

waters that conjures

a liquid wall to

crush any enemies

that oppose him.

name: Kagemusha of the Blue Flame
description:
Serves as a double

for the ruler of the

Blue Flame. A master

swordsman that

wields a fine blade.

name: Flame Ghost
description:
A fiery spirit

that burns anything

in its path.

name: Dryad
description:
A spirit of the

forest protected by

the surrounding

plant life.

name: B. Skull Dragon
description:
A very rare creature

created from the

fusion of an

uncommon beast and

a vicious dragon.

name: Two-mouth Darkruler
description:
A dinosaur with two

crushing jaws.

Stores electricity

in its horn and

releases high

voltage bolts

from the mouth

on its back.

name: Solitude
description:
A beast-warrior that

swings a massive

scythe that draws on

the spirit of its

enemies to deliver

devastating blows.

name: Masked Sorcerer
description:
A mysterious wizard

whose face remains

forever hidden

behind a strange

mask.

name: Kumootoko
description:
A massive,

intelligent spider

that traps its

enemies with webbing.

name: Midnight Fiend
description:
A winged creature

rumored to appear

at midnight.

name: Roaring Ocean Snake
description:
A massive

sea serpent that

creates tidal waves

to wipe out

its enemies.

name: Trap Master
description:
A warrior that

excels in laying

traps such as a

bottomless pit, for

eternally ensnaring

opponents.

name: Fiend Sword
description:
Few have escaped

the curse of this

creature. Those that

have done so have

gained untold power.

name: Skull Stalker
description:
Swift and vicious,

this monster grabs

its victim with its

pincers and attacks

the captive with its

poison stinger.

name: Hitodenchak
description:
A vicious starfish

that spits acid

to melt away

its enemies.

name: Wood Remains
description:
A zombie that rose

from the remains of

the woodland ruler.

name: Hourglass of Life
description:
A creature

that allows power

to be gained

at the cost of life.

name: Rare Fish
description:
An unusual and

ferocious fish with

the head of a beast.

name: Wood Clown
description:
An unpleasantly

smiling creature

that wields a scythe

to avoid enemy blows.

name: Madjinn Gunn
description:
A living weapon that

fires projectiles

from its mouth.

name: Dark Titan of Terror
description:
A spirit said to

dwell in the world

of dreams.

Attacks enemies

in their sleep.

name: Beautiful Headhuntress
description:
A lovely swordmaster

with some very

agile moves.

name: Wodan the Resident of the Forest
description:
A warrior that has

long resided in the

forest and enjoys

the protection

of Mother Nature.

name: Guardian of the Labyrinth
description:
A warrior that

guards the entrance

to the netherworld.

name: Haniwa
description:
An earthen doll

that protects

the treasure

in the tombs

of ancient kings.

name: Yashinoki
description:
A palm tree with a

will of its own that

attacks enemies by

flinging coconuts.

name: Vishwar Randi
description:
A woman warrior that

serves the forces

of darkness.

name: The Drdek
description:
An eyeball creature

with legs for

jumping high and

delivering finishing

blows with its sharp

claws.

name: Dark Assailant
description:
Armed with Psycho

Sword, this sinister

cutthroat rules the

outer land.

name: Candle of Fate
description:
An opponent's fate

is decided

when the flames

of each finger

are extinguished.

name: Water Element
description:
A water spirit

that envelops

its opponent

in a thick fog

to cover its attack.

name: Dissolverock
description:
A monster borne from

the lava pits.

Generates intensive

heat that can melt

away its enemies.

name: Meda Bat
description:
An eyeball fiend

created by a servant

of darkness.

Uses "Dark Spheres"

to blow away

its enemies.

name: One Who Hunts Souls
description:
A creature

with a sword

that gains its power

from the life forces

of its victims.

name: Root Water
description:
An amphibian capable

of calling up a

massive tidal wave

from the dark seas

to wipe out enemy

monsters.

name: Master & Expert
description:
A fearsome duo

consisting of a

beast master and

its loyal servant.

name: Water Omotics
description:
Transforms the water

overflowing from a

jar into attacking

dragons.

name: Hyo
description:
An ice warrior whose

slightest touch

freezes an opponent.

name: Enchanting Mermaid
description:
A beautiful mermaid

that lures voyagers

to a watery grave.

name: Nekogal #1
description:
A cat creature that

looks cute to the

eye but delivers

scratching blows

with its sharp claws.

name: Angelwitch
description:
A creature

that chose the

path of sorcery

to become a witch.

name: Embryonic Beast
description:
A repulsive monster

with a gaping belly

that swallows almost

anything.

name: Prevent Rat
description:
This monster is

shielded by 

a hide covered

in thick hair.

name: Dimensional Warrior
description:
A monster

capable of creating

dimensional rifts

to trap its enemies.

name: Stone Armadiller
description:
With a body armored

by rock-hard fur,

this monster

features excellent

defense capabilities.

name: Beastking of the Swamps
description:
This creature

changes the ground

at its feet into

quicksand to ensnare

its enemies.

name: Ancient Sorcerer
description:
A master fighter

that uses various

staffs to render

enemies unconscious.

name: Lunar Queen Elzaim
description:
A lovely

moon goddess that

can throw up

a lunar curtain

to block

enemy attacks.

name: Wicked Mirror
description:
A malevolent mirror

that hypnotizes

a beholder and

renders the victim

susceptible

to attacks.

name: The Little Swordsman of Aile
description:
An elf warrior

mounted on a huge

lizard.

name: Rock Ogre Grotto #2
description:
A stone golem

that turns opponents

into rocks and

crushes them to dust.

name: Wing Egg Elf
description:
Hiding within its

eggshell, this

creature blocks

enemy attacks with

its massive wings.

name: The Furious Sea King
description:
Grand King of the

Seven Seas.

Able to summon

massive tidal waves

to drown the enemy.

name: Princess of Tsurugi
description:
A queen of swords

that is virtually

unequalled in her

mastery of every

blade imaginable

to man.

name: Unknown Warrior of Fiend
description:
The speed of this

warrior creates

an intense vacuum

that can actually

slice through

a monster's hide.

name: Sectarian of Secrets
description:
A sorcerer that

worships the dark

forces and can

summon a massive

hand to drag away

opponents into

the netherworld.

name: Versago the Destroyer
description:
A lord of

destruction

born from the heart

of darkness,

this creature

can summon storms

to destroy opponents.

name: Wetha
description:
A rain spirit that

can summon typhoons

to blow away its

enemies.

name: Megirus Light
description:
This creature's

ominous eyes can

unleash piercing

rays against its

enemies.

name: Mavelus
description:
Related to the

phoenix, this

creature dwells in

the mountains. Its

fiery breath is

extremely scorching.

name: Ancient Tree of Enlightenment
description:
Armed with a wealth

of knowledge, this

monster is able to

block just about

any attack.

name: Green Phantom King
description:
This youthful king

of the forests lives

in a green world,

abundant with trees

and wildlife.

name: Ground Attacker Bugroth
description:
A land-based armored

robot that is said

to once have marine

attack capabilities.

name: Ray & Temperature
description:
The Sun and the

North Wind join

hands to deliver

a devastating

combination of heat

and gale-force winds.

name: Gorgon Egg
description:
A gorgon's egg with

eyes said to create

whatever creature

crosses its view.

name: Petit Moth
description:
Nobody has any idea

what creature may

spawn from this

mysterious larva.

name: King Fog
description:
A spectre that

dwells in a blinding

curtain of smoke.

name: Protector of the Throne
description:
A creature that

protects the king's

throne from usurpers.

name: Mystic Clown
description:
Nothing can stop the

mad attack of this

powerful creature.

name: Mystical Sheep #2
description:
A monstrous sheep

with a long tail for

hypnotizing enemies

to render them

powerless.

name: Holograh
description:
A monster machine

that generates

images to confuse

its enemies,

making them prone

to attacks.

name: Tao the Chanter
description:
A magic-user that

corrodes the yin

and yang to create

a twisted power

to attack enemies.

name: Serpent Marauder
description:
A snake with a

single eye that

blows an icy breath

to freeze its

opponents.

name: Gatekeeper
description:
An indestructible

machine

built to protect

key entrances.

name: Ogre of the Black Shadow
description:
An ogre possessed

by the powers

of the dark.

Few can withstand

its rapid charge.

name: Dark Artist
description:
A demented artist

that creates

objets d'art

to crush enemies.

name: Change Slime
description:
A shape-shifting

slime that is

capable of adopting

the form of other

creatures.

name: Moon Envoy
description:
A servant of the

moon goddess,

this warrior

wields a pike

with a spectacular

crescent-shaped

blade.

name: Fireyarou
description:
A malevolent

creature

wrapped in flames

that attacks enemies

with intense fire.

name: Psychic Kappa
description:
An amphibian with

extrasensory powers

for blocking attacks.

name: Masaki the Legendary Swordsman
description:
Legendary

swordmaster and a

veteran of over 100

battles.

name: Dragoness the Wicked Knight
description:
A warrior

equipped with

equipment fashioned

from dragon scales.

name: Bio Plant
description:
A monstrous creature

born from a failed

lab experiment.

name: One-eyed Shield Dragon
description:
This dragon wears a

shield not only for

its own protection

but also for ramming

its enemies.

name: Cyber Soldier of Darkworld
description:
An unstoppable

mechanical soldier

powered by dark

forces.

name: Wicked Dragon with the Ersatz Head
description:
A two-headed dragon

with a pair of

vicious jaws for

crushing its enemies.

name: Sonic Maid
description:
A maiden

that uses sound

to her advantage.

She wields a scythe

that's shaped

like a musical note.

name: Kurama
description:
A vicious bird that

attacks from the

skies with its

whip-like tail.

name: Legendary Sword
description:
A sword that brings

out the best in

warriors. It cannot

be used by servants

of the dark.

name: Sword of Dark Destruction
description:
Dark forces

increase the power

of Warriors!

name: Dark Energy
description:
Dark forces increase

the power of Fiends

and other monsters

of the Dark!

name: Axe of Despair
description:
Fiends and

Beast-Warriors can

constantly use their

maximum strength!

name: Laser Cannon Armor
description:
Arms Insects with

a powerful laser!

name: Insect Armor with Laser Cannon
description:
Allows Insects to

fire an intense

blast of fire!

name: Elf's Light
description:
Increases the power

of elves with

mystical light!

name: Beast Fangs
description:
Increases the power

of Beasts and other

fanged monsters!

name: Steel Shell
description:
Boosts the power of

shelled monsters!

Said to have no

effect on those

without shells.

name: Vile Germs
description:
Vile microbes boost

the power of Plants

in the woods!

name: Black Pendant
description:
This pendant grants

extra power

to Dark sorcerers!

name: Silver Bow and Arrow
description:
Silver bow and arrow

enhances the power

of Fairies.

name: Horn of Light
description:
Increases the power

of horned creatures!

Has no effect

on Dark monsters.

name: Horn of the Unicorn
description:
Increases the power

of Dark monsters

with horns!

name: Dragon Treasure
description:
A legendary treasure

that increases the

power of dragons.

name: Electro-whip
description:
A whip for

paralyzing enemies.

Increases power when

equipped with

female creatures.

name: Cyber Shield
description:
Increases the power

of female monsters

by changing their

attitudes.

name: Elegant Egotist
description:
Creates two

doppelgangers of

Harpy Lady for

three-pronged

attacks!

name: Mystical Moon
description:
Moonlight increases

the power of Beasts!

name: Stop Defense
description:
Forces an opponent's

monster card

positioned for

defense into the

attack position.

name: Malevolent Nuzzler
description:
Diabolic forces act

to increase the

power of female and

Dark monsters!

name: Violet Crystal
description:
Mystic forces from

the crystal increase

the power of Zombies.

name: Book of Secret Arts
description:
A magic book for

increasing the power

of magic-users.

It cannot be used

by bad-hearted

sorcerers.

name: Invigoration
description:
Increases the power

of Thunder, Rock,

and Pyro monsters.

name: Machine Conversion Factory
description:
A manufacturing

facility that tunes

up all Machine

monsters.

name: Raise Body Heat
description:
Absorbs the sun's

energy to increase

the power of

Dinosaurs!

name: Follow Wind
description:
The winds provide

support to increase

the power of Winged

Beasts and other

flying monsters!

name: Power of Kaishin
description:
Poseidon's Strength

is shared to boost

the power of

Aqua, Fish, and

Sea Serpent

monsters!

name: Dragon Capture Jar
description:
Destroys

all opponent

Dragon monsters

on the playfield!

name: Forest
description:
Changes the field

in favor of

Beast-Warrior,

Insect, Plant, and

Beast monsters!

name: Wasteland
description:
Changes the field

in favor of Zombie,

Dinosaur and

Rock monsters!

name: Mountain
description:
Changes the field

in favor of Dragon,

Winged Beast, and

Thunder monsters!

name: Sogen
description:
Changes the field

to meadow land

in favor of Warrior

and Beast-Warrior

monsters!

name: Umi
description:
Changes the field

in favor of Aqua

and Thunder monsters,

but unfavorable to

Machine and Pyro

monsters!

name: Yami
description:
Changes the field

in favor of

Magic-User and

Fiend monsters,

but unfavorable

to Fairy monsters!

name: Dark Hole
description:
Sucks up every card

in play on the field!

name: Raigeki
description:
Destroys every

opposing monster

with a stroke

of lightning!

name: Mooyan Curry
description:
A delicious

beef curry increases

Life Points by 200!

name: Red Medicine
description:
A magic potion

that increases

Life Points by 500!

name: Goblin's Secret Remedy
description:
A goblin's herb

that increases

Life Points by 1000!

name: Soul of the Pure
description:
A fairy potion

that increases

Life Points by 2000!

name: Dian Keto the Cure Master
description:
A mystical power

that increases

Life Points by 5000!

name: Sparks
description:
A shower of sparks

inflicts 50 points

of damage

to your opponent's

Life Points!!

name: Hinotama
description:
A fireball

inflicts 100 points

of damage

to your opponent's

Life Points!!

name: Final Flame
description:
Flames

inflict 200 points

of damage

to your opponent's

Life Points!!

name: Ookazi
description:
Flames

inflict 500 points

of damage

to your opponent's

Life Points!

name: Tremendous Fire
description:
An inferno

inflicts 1000 points

of damage

to your opponent's

Life Points!

name: Swords of Revealing Light
description:
Enemy monsters

are revealed and

your opponent

cannot attack

for three turns.

name: Spellbinding Circle
description:
A curse reduces the

power of all enemy

monsters!

name: Dark-piercing Light
description:
A dazzling light

reveals all monsters

on the playing field.

name: Yaranzo
description:
A monster that

attacks anybody

who attempts

to open its lid.

name: Kanan the Swordmistress
description:
A lady swordsman

that floats like a

butterfly and stings

like a bee.

name: Takriminos
description:
A finned creature

distantly related

to sea Dragons.

name: Stuffed Animal
description:
A deceptively cute

stuffed animal that

bites.

name: Megasonic Eye
description:
A cryptic doomsday

machine that comes

from the edge of

the universe.

name: Super War-lion
description:
A very vicious lion

with sharp and

long claws.

name: Yamadron
description:
A three-headed,

fire-breathing

monster.

name: Seiyaryu
description:
A sacred dragon

that burns away

wickedness with its

mystical flames.

name: Three-legged Zombies
description:
Bony and Tubby,

a friendly pair

of skeletons.

name: Zera The Mant
description:
A huge, brutal

monster that attacks

with razor-sharp

claws.

name: Flying Penguin
description:
A rare penguin that

flies with the wings

on its head.

name: Millennium Shield
description:
A Millennium Item

candidate

that is said

to block any

powerful attack.

name: Fairy's Gift
description:
Flies around

spreading happiness

to all.

name: Black Luster Soldier
description:
A powerful warrior

with the same

capabilities as the

legendary Blue-eyes

White Dragon.

name: Fiend's Mirror
description:
An arcane glass

that draws

its enemies into

the mirror world.

name: Labyrinth Wall
description:
Walls appear

on the field to form

a labyrinth with

no exit.

name: Jirai Gumo
description:
A monster spider

that dwells

under the earth.

name: Shadow Ghoul
description:
A dangerous zombie

that crawls

in the dark.

name: Wall Shadow
description:
An unusually fast

monster that sweeps

across walls to

attack its enemies.

name: Labyrinth Tank
description:
A tank that races

around a labyrinth

hunting down

its enemies.

name: Sanga of the Thunder
description:
A golem that uses

lightning attacks

similar to the

Labyrinth Brothers.

name: Kazejin
description:
A golem that

controls the winds

like the Labyrinth

Brothers.

name: Suijin
description:
A golem that uses

water attacks like

the Labyrinth

Brothers.

name: Gate Guardian
description:
Sanga, Kazejin, and

Suijin join to

form a single,

powerful monster.

name: Dungeon Worm
description:
Hidden under

the floors of

a labyrinth,

it swallows any

who pass above.

name: Monster Tamer
description:
A master of monsters

that exercises

control over several

creatures.

name: Ryu-kishin Powered
description:
Ryu-kishin enhanced

by the powers of

darkness. Very sharp

talons make it

a worthy opponent.

name: Swordstalker
description:
A monster formed by

the vengeful souls

of those who passed

away in battle.

name: La Jinn the Mystical Genie
description:
A genie of the lamp

that's at the beck

and call of its

master.

name: Blue-eyes Ultimate Dragon
description:
The ultimate dragon

formed by the fusion

of three Blue-eyes

White Dragons.

name: Toon Alligator
description:
An alligator monster

straight from

the cartoons.

name: Rude Kaiser
description:
With an axe in each

hand, this monster

delivers heavy

damage.

name: Parrot Dragon
description:
A dragon from the

cartoons that's more

dangerous than it

appears to be.

name: Dark Rabbit
description:
A cartoon rabbit

that quickly leaps

all over the place,

making it a

difficult target.

name: Bickuribox
description:
A jack-in-the-box

that excels

in surprise attacks.

name: Harpie's Pet Dragon
description:
A favorite pet for

harpies, but a very

dangerous dragon.

name: Mystic Lamp
description:
A lamp

used by wizards

to mix potions.

name: Pendulum Machine
description:
A horrible torture

machine with a large

pendulum blade.

name: Giltia the D. Knight
description:
Armed with a

soul-searing spear,

this creature favors

magic attacks.

name: Launcher Spider
description:
A spider machine

that launches

explosive rockets

against its enemies.

name: Zoa
description:
A monster

whose full potential

can be achieved

when transformed

into its metal form.

name: Metalzoa
description:
A metallic Zoa

capable of

intensive attacks.

name: Zone Eater
description:
A sea creature that

swallows enemies and

slowly digests them.

name: Steel Scorpion
description:
An iron-tailed

monster equipped

with very sharp

scissors.

name: Dancing Elf
description:
An elf that dances

across the sky with

wings of razor-sharp

blades.

name: Ocubeam
description:
Frightening in

appearance, this

creature uses its

large eyes and ears

to keep track

of any movement.

name: Leghul
description:
Not a very powerful

monster despite its

large fangs and

spikes.

name: Ooguchi
description:
A monstrous bullfrog

with poison spikes.

name: Swordsman from a Foreign Land
description:
An eastern warrior

armed with a cursed

sword.

name: Emperor of the Land and Sea
description:
A fire-breathing

reptilian monster.

name: Ushi Oni
description:
A bull monster

resurrected by

the dark arts

that appears

from inside a jar.

name: Monster Eye
description:
A servant that

maintains a close

watch on anything

and everything.

It throws up

a smokescreen

when discovered.

name: Leogun
description:
Huge monster

with a lion's mane

similar to the

"King of Beasts".

name: Tatsunootoshigo
description:
A fast-moving sea

monster that has the

bodies of a horse

and a fish.

name: Saber Slasher
description:
A rampaging machine

that wields

a massive sword.

name: Yaiba Robo
description:
A machine

with several blades

hidden within

its square body.

name: Machine King
description:
Armored with super

alloy, this robot

attacks with blasts

of fire launched

from both arms.

name: Giant Mech-soldier
description:
This monster swings

an earth-shaking axe

that can eliminate

enemies with

a single blow.

name: Metal Dragon
description:
A golden,

fire-breathing

dragon that burns

any opponent

in its path.

name: Mechanical Spider
description:
A spider-shaped,

mechanized monster

with sickles at

the end of its legs.

name: Bat
description:
A mechanized bat

that attacks

by dropping

explosion orbs.

name: Giga-tech Wolf
description:
A wolf made entirely

of iron. Its steel

jaws can bite

through anything.

name: Cyber Soldier
description:
Round-shaped

soldiers that roll

around and act as

guardians to the

Machine King.

name: Shovel Crusher
description:
Armed with

a pair of shovels,

this creature is

a walking engine

of destruction.

name: Mechanicalchacer
description:
A hunter that

relentlessly pursues

its target by order

of the Machine King.

name: Blocker
description:
Each separate part

of this creature is

an individual weapon

capable of

devastating attacks.

name: Blast Juggler
description:
A walking time

device that loves

to blow enemies

away.

name: Golgoil
description:
A massive iron golem

that appears from

a dimensional rift.

name: Giganto
description:
This creature swings

around a huge spiked

ball to destroy its

enemies.

name: Cyber-Stein
description:
Created in a

basement lab, this

infernal machine

launches rockets

from within its

mouth.

name: Cyber Commander
description:
A strike force

equipped with

rader detectors

and sensors.

name: Jinzo #7
description:
Created in an

underground lab,

this artificial

being occasionally

goes berserk.

name: Dice Armadillo
description:
An armadillo-like

creature that forms

a die whenever it

rolls up its body.

name: Sky Dragon
description:
A bird-like dragon

with four bladed

wings.

name: Thunder Dragon
description:
A dragon that

summons thunder and

lightning to attack

its opponents.

name: Stone D.
description:
With a body

consisting entirely

of rocks, 

this dragon

flings boulders

at its enemies.

name: Kaiser Dragon
description:
A very proud and

powerful dragon

emperor.

name: Magician of Faith
description:
Despite its weak

strength, this

creature is capable

of casting spells

to eliminate

darkness.

name: Goddess of Whim
description:
A shy goddess that

seems to spend the

majority of her

time sleeping.

name: Water Magician
description:
This creature

surrounds opponents

with water and

envelops them in a

sweeping attack.

name: Ice Water
description:
A very aggressive

mermaid with spikes

for attacking

enemies.

name: Waterdragon Fairy
description:
A fairy that

wanders the seas.

Rumored to have

the capabilities

for summoning sea

dragons.

name: Ancient Elf
description:
This elf is rumored

to have lived for

thousands of years.

He leads an army of

spirits against his

enemies.

name: Beautiful Beast Trainer
description:
A rare female

magic-user armed

with a vicious whip.

name: Water Girl
description:
A beautiful creature

that flings icy

arrows.

name: White Dolphin
description:
A white, horned

dolphin that attacks

by calling up

tidal waves.

name: Deepsea Shark
description:
A violent shark that

attacks anything

in the sea.

name: Metal Fish
description:
A steel fish

armed with a sharp

dorsal fin.

name: Bottom Dweller
description:
A beautiful swimmer

with a very nasty

temperament.

name: 7 Colored Fish
description:
A rare rainbow fish

that is almost

impossible to catch.

name: Mech Bass
description:
This creature

carries a plasma

cannon on its back.

name: Aqua Dragon
description:
A dragon that dwells

in the sea. It is

capable of spitting

high-pressure blasts

of water.

name: Sea King Dragon
description:
The king of the seas,

this creature is

protected by a solid

shell and spits

poisonous bubbles at

its enemies.

name: Turu-Purun
description:
A strange, one-eyed

monster armed with

a dangerous spear.

name: Guardian of the Sea
description:
A merman warrior

that attacks anyone

who dares to

pollute the sea.

name: Aqua Snake
description:
A creature that

drowns its opponents

by mesmerizing them

with the ball on

the end of its tail.

name: Giant Red Seasnake
description:
A sea serpent

that bites anything

that passes nearby.

name: Spike Seadra
description:
Using the spikes

sprouting from its

body, this creature

stabs its opponents

and floods them

with electricity.

name: 30,000-Year White Turtle
description:
A massive and

well-protected

giant turtle

that has lived

over 30000 years.

name: Kappa Avenger
description:
An amphibian sworn

to avenge the death

of its brothers.

name: Kanikabuto
description:
A crab monster with

two massive scissors

for cutting up

enemies.

name: Zarigun
description:
A newly evolved

crayfish with sharp

scissors for

clipping the enemy.

name: Millennium Golem
description:
A golem

that has protected

treasure for nearly

a millennium.

name: Destroyer Golem
description:
A golem with a

massive right hand

for crushing its

victims.

name: Barrel Rock
description:
A monster that

charges into enemies

firing a pair of

cannons mounted on

its shoulders.

name: Minomushi Warrior
description:
A rock warrior

that wields

a very heavy sword

carved from stone.

name: Stone Ghost
description:
A creature that

erupts with anger,

resulting in a

crushing rain of

boulders.

name: Kaminari Attack
description:
A monster that

judges wrong-doers

and punishes them

appropriately.

name: Tripwire Beast
description:
This creature

attacks enemies

with electromagnetic

waves.

name: Bolt Escargot
description:
This creature spits

a gooey substance

that robs enemies of

mobility and then

stuns them with

electric shocks.

name: Bolt Penguin
description:
A monster

with a pair of

electric whips

instead of arms.

name: The Immortal of Thunder
description:
A creature that

attacks enemies

with thunderbolts.

name: Electric Snake
description:
A serpent with a

tail for storing

electricity.

name: Wing Eagle
description:
A hunter of the

skies that has never

missed a target.

name: Punished Eagle
description:
A judge of the skies

that delivers

a sentence with

its punishing

silver-white claws.

name: Skull Red Bird
description:
This monster

swoops down

and attacks with

a rain of knives

stored in its wings.

name: Crimson Sunbird
description:
A monster burning

with crimson flames

and capable of

delivering a rain of

sparks by flapping

its wings.

name: Queen Bird
description:
A creature that

attacks its enemies

with its large beak.

name: Armed Ninja
description:
A blue ninja

that attacks

with a large sickle

and spiked feet.

name: Magical Ghost
description:
This creature casts

a spell of terror

and confusion just

before attacking

its enemies.

name: Soul Hunter
description:
This clown feeds

the life force of

its enemies to

a monstrous lizard.

name: Air Eater
description:
A monster that

suffocates its

enemy by feeding

on the surrounding

air supply.

name: Vermillion Sparrow
description:
A fiery warrior

creature that

unleashes intense

heat from its body.

name: Sea Kamen
description:
A cruel monster that

slices up enemies

with its sharp claws.

name: Sinister Serpent
description:
A flying poison

snake that is

not very good

at maneuvering

on the ground.

name: Ganigumo
description:
A spider armed with

scissors to attack

anything that

it traps in its web.

name: Alinsection
description:
A stag beetle

monster with

saw-toothed horn

and arms.

name: Insect Soldiers of the Sky
description:
Insect soldiers that

attack in swarms.

name: Cockroach Knight
description:
A cockroach warrior

that hides in small

spaces and emerges

to attack enemies.

name: Kuwagata a
description:
A violent stag

beetle with a 

razor-like cutter.

name: Burglar
description:
A clever mouse

with a sharpened

left claw.

name: Pragtical
description:
A very dangerous

monster with spikes

on its head and tail.

name: Garvas
description:
A malevolent

creature that

resembles a

winged lion.

name: Ameba
description:
A monster

that envelops

an enemy and

slowly digests it.

name: Korogashi
description:
This creature rolls

massive objects

to crush its enemies.

name: Boo Koo
description:
A book wizard

with page after page

of potent spells.

name: Flower Wolf
description:
A beast

covered in flowers

from head to toe.

name: Rainbow Flower
description:
A flower creature

with rainbow-colored

blossoms that lure

an enemy into its

waiting jaws.

name: Barrel Lily
description:
A dangerous flower

that fires pollen

projectiles.

name: Needle Ball
description:
A ball covered in

sharp needles.

Usually rains down

on enemies in a

group.

name: Peacock
description:
A beautiful peacock-

like creature that

fires its feathers

at opponents.

name: Hoshiningen
description:
Trailed by a

beautiful tail, this

shooting star

inflicts damage when

it hits an enemy.

name: Maha Vailo
description:
A wizard dressed in

blue who is usually

found meditating.

name: Rainbow Marine Mermaid
description:
An unusual mermaid

that appears

whenever a rainbow

bridges the sky.

name: Musician King
description:
A fantastic guitar

player that attacks

enemies with

ultrasonic emissions.

name: Wilmee
description:
A ferocious rabbit

with sharp claws.

name: Yado Karu
description:
A hermit crab with

the head of a dragon.

name: Morinphen
description:
A strange fiend

with long arms and

razor-sharp talons.

name: Kattapillar
description:
Attacks by blowing

webs at its enemies.

Nobody knows

what the final form

of this insect

might be.

name: Dragon Seeker
description:
A fearsome monster

sent from the

netherworld

to destroy dragons.

name: Man-eater Bug
description:
A creature that

slices and dices

with its scissors

and feeds off its

victims.

name: D. Human
description:
Gifted with the

power of dragons,

this warrior wields

a sword created

from a dragon's fang.

name: Turtle Raccoon
description:
A fox-like creature

with a protective

shell.

name: Fungi of the Musk
description:
A monster that leaks

acid from its pores

to melt anything

that touches its

skin.

name: Prisman
description:
A clear crystal

that focuses light

to create a powerful

laser beam.

name: Gale Dogra
description:
A huge moth that

generates a

whirlwind containing

poison dust.

name: Crazy Fish
description:
A flying fish

with a sharp head

for piercing targets.

name: Cyber Saurus
description:
A mechanical

dinosaur equipped

with a beam cannon.

name: Bracchio-raidus
description:
A colossal dinosaur

that stomps

on anything

that wanders

into its path.

name: Laughing Flower
description:
A laughing flower

whose chuckles can

drive an enemy mad.

name: Bean Soldier
description:
A plant warrior

that attacks

with a combination

of sword-swings and

pea projectiles.

name: Cannon Soldier
description:
A highly destructive

machine armed with a

powerful cannon.

name: Guardian of the Throne Room
description:
A sentry robot armed

with homing rockets

for guarding throne

rooms from intruders.

name: Brave Scizzar
description:
A creature capable

of manipulating

several scissors

with definite

results.

name: The Statue of Easter Island
description:
A massive stone idol

from Easter Island

that fires laser

rings from its mouth.

name: Muka Muka
description:
A monster that

angers an opponent

to the point that

the enemy goes

berserk.

name: Sand Stone
description:
Appears from

underground and

attacks with long,

snake-like tentacles.

name: Boulder Tortoise
description:
A stone turtle with

a very high defense

factor.

name: Fire Kraken
description:
A fiery squid that

can maintain its

flames underwater.

name: Turtle Bird
description:
A rare flying turtle

that inhabits

the sea.

name: Skullbird
description:
The breath from this

bird robs creatures

of their life force.

name: Monstrous Bird
description:
A huge bird

known for its sharp

dive attacks.

name: The Bistro Butcher
description:
Defeated enemies

serve as ingredients

for this gourmet

monster.

name: Star Boy
description:
An extraterrestrial

life form that loves

living in water.

name: Spirit of the Mountain
description:
Music from this

creature's flute

can drain 

an enemy's willpower.

name: Neck Hunter
description:
Armed with a huge

sickle, this monster

can fire beams

from its large eyes.

name: Milus Radiant
description:
Often mistaken

as a cute pet,

this creature is a

very dangerous beast.

name: Togex
description:
A very fast monster

that rolls up and

rams its enemies.

name: Flame Cerebrus
description:
A flaming beast

that is lethal

to the touch.

name: Eldeen
description:
Uses a wand to cast

various spells

against an enemy.

name: Mystical Sand
description:
Turns enemies to

stone and crushes

them to dust.

name: Gemini Elf
description:
Elf twins

that attack an enemy

from opposite sides.

name: Kwagar Hercules
description:
An insect monster

with the jaws of

a stag beetle and

the horn of a beetle.

name: Minar
description:
A monster with four

highly dexterous

arms for executing

separate attacks.

name: Kamakiriman
description:
A man-shaped mantis

with two razor-sharp

scythes.

name: Mechaleon
description:
A chameleon-like

monster that can

hide anywhere

by changing colors.

name: Mega Thunderball
description:
Rolls along the

ground releasing

bolts of electricity

to attack its

enemies.

name: Niwatori
description:
Swallows enemies

whole and uses

their essence

as energy.

name: Corroding Shark
description:
A zombie shark that

wanders the ocean

depths, cursing any

that dare cross its

path.

name: Skelengel
description:
A phantom fairy that

fires countless

arrows at anything

that harbors an urge

to attack.

name: Hane-Hane
description:
This creature blocks

enemy movement with

gale-force winds

and attacks with

a massive battle axe.

name: Misairuzame
description:
A rocket-launching

fish protected

by thorny spikes.

name: Tongyo
description:
This creature is

powered by the life

force of the fishes

it captures with

its long tongue.

name: Dharma Cannon
description:
A highly accurate

mechanical monster

covered with large-

caliber cannons.

name: Skelgon
description:
A skeletal zombie

dragon that is

capable of flying

across the skies.

name: Wow Warrior
description:
A massive beast

of a fish with

arms, legs, and 

razor-sharp teeth.

name: Griggle
description:
This monster spins

about its enemy

launching blinding

leaves and painful

seeds.

name: Bone Mouse
description:
A zombie rat

that hunts felines.

name: Frog The Jam
description:
A slime creature

with a frog's head

that croaks as it

attacks.

name: Behegon
description:
A strange sea

serpent with a

massive mouth lined

with huge fangs.

name: Dark Elf
description:
A wicked elf

that just loves

to engage in battle.

name: Winged Dragon #2
description:
Creates powerful

tornadoes with

its huge wings.

name: Mushroom Man #2
description:
A fully grown

Mushroom Man with

an increased

attack factor.

name: Lava Battleguard
description:
This brother of

Swamp Battleguard

may not be powerful,

but is pretty good

on defense.

name: Tyhone #2
description:
A crimson dragon

that spits fireballs

at its enemies.

name: The Wandering Doomed
description:
A monster that

aimlessly wanders

in search of enemies.

name: Steel Ogre Grotto #1
description:
A steel idol

worshipped in the

Land of Machines.

name: Pot the Trick
description:
A not very reliable

sorcerer's servant.

name: Oscillo Hero
description:
A strange warrior

from another

dimension.

name: Invader from Another Dimension
description:
A creature that came

from another galaxy.

name: Lesser Dragon
description:
A low-class, minor

dragon incapable

of breathing fire.

name: Needle Worm
description:
A larva

with steel spikes

to attack the unwary.

name: Wretched Ghost of the Attic
description:
A harmless creature

usually found

in the attic

of any home.

name: Great Mammoth of Goldfine
description:
A very unusual

skeletal zombie

elephant with

glowing gold bones.

name: Man-eating Black Shark
description:
A black shark

that can detect

almost any scent

in the water.

name: Yormungarde
description:
A very long snake

that often appears

in legends and myths.

name: Darkworld Thorns
description:
A thorny plant found

in the darklands

that wraps itself

around any unwary

traveler.

name: Anthrosaurus
description:
Man-like dinosaur

lacking in strength,

but with a high I.Q.

name: Drooling Lizard
description:
A blood-sucking

snake in human form

that attacks any

living being that

passes nearby.

name: Trakadon
description:
A tiger-striped

dragon that is often

seen racing across

the wasteland with

tremendous speed.

name: B. Dragon Jungle King
description:
A jet-black dragon

that inhabits the

jungles and feeds

on trees.

name: Empress Judge
description:
Empress of the

Golden Kingdom. None

may refuse her will.

name: Little D
description:
A very ferocious

monster spawned

from a T-Rex.

name: Witch of the Black Forest
description:
This forest-dwelling

witch can see all

with the eye

on her forehead.

name: Ancient One of the Deep Forest
description:
A white goat that

has inhabited the

forest for ages.

The creature is

actually an elder

of the woods.

name: Giant Scorpion of the Tundra
description:
A rare scarlet

scorpion that can be

found in the tundra

-- not in the desert.

name: Crow Goblin
description:
A very wise,

long-nosed goblin

with supernatural

powers.

name: Leo Wizard
description:
A wizard with a

black cape that is

actually a talking

lion disguised

as a man.

name: Abyss Flower
description:
A rare flower

that blooms in a

pitch-dark abyss.

name: Patrol Robo
description:
A cutting-edge robot

that eliminates

intruders upon

detection.

name: Takuhee
description:
This bird is

a precursor

to disaster!!

name: Dark Witch
description:
A popular creature

in mythology that

delivers judgement

with a sharp spear.

name: Weather Report
description:
This creature is

known to predict the

weather with very

little accuracy.

name: Binding Chain
description:
This creature

corners its enemies

and seals away

their power.

name: Mechanical Snail
description:
A mechanically

enhanced snail that

is no faster than

it used to be.

name: Greenkappa
description:
A creature that

transforms into the

image of its enemy

and copies every

offensive move.

name: Mon Larvas
description:
A highly evolved

Larvas that is even

more powerful than

before.

name: Living Vase
description:
A living vase that

blinds enemies with

pollen and attacks

with its sharp teeth.

name: Tentacle Plant
description:
Attacks a nearby

opponent by reaching

out with its blue

vines.

name: Beaked Snake
description:
Wraps its coils

around opponents and

pecks them with its

huge beak.

name: Morphing Jar
description:
A large jar

that attacks

nearby enemies

by unleashing

the monster

it contains inside.

name: Muse-A
description:
A fairy of the arts

and an excellent

harp player.

name: Giant Turtle Who Feeds on Flames
description:
A monster turtle

with a crimson shell.

It feeds on fire.

name: Rose Spectre of Dunn
description:
A red rose possessed

by a vile spirit

that feeds on

the life force

of others to

provide the flower

with nourishment.

name: Fiend Refrection #1
description:
Drags enemies into

a mirror world.

name: Ghoul with an Appetite
description:
A monster that can

eat all it wants but

is never fulfilled.

name: Pale Beast
description:
With skin tinged

a bluish white, this

strange creature is

a fearsome sight

to behold.

name: Little Chimera
description:
A monster created

from an experimental

attempt to graft

wings on beasts.

name: Violent Rain
description:
A monster capable of

bringing on sudden

rain showers.

name: Key Mace #2
description:
Seals away the good

in a soul to create

a wicked being.

name: Tenderness
description:
A cute fairy

dedicated

to bringing

about eternal love.

name: Penguin Soldier
description:
A low-class penguin

soldier that attacks

in a group.

name: Fairy Dragon
description:
A beautiful

and powerful

dragon fairy.

name: Obese Marmot of Nefariousness
description:
An ill-mannered

field mouse that

chews on anything.

name: Liquid Beast
description:
A liquid life form

that moves freely

in water.

name: Twin Long Rods #2
description:
An undersea creature

that attacks with

two whip-like tails.

name: Great Bill
description:
A monster with a

massive maw that

allows it to swallow

an enemy whole.

name: Shining Friendship
description:
The peacemaker

among monsters.

name: Bladefly
description:
A monster fly

that swoops down

with sharp

sword-like arms

extended out front.

name: Electric Lizard
description:
A lizard

that discharges

electricity stored

in its body.

name: Hiro's Shadow Scout
description:
A servant of fiends

used primarily for

scouting an area.

name: Lady of Faith
description:
Soothes the souls of

others by chanting

a mysterious spell.

name: Twin-headed Thunder Dragon
description:
A two-headed Thunder

Dragon capable of

powerful electric

attacks.

name: Hunter Spider
description:
A hunter that uses

its spider web to

entrap its enemies.

name: Armored Starfish
description:
A bluish starfish

with a solid hide

capable of fending

off attacks.

name: Hourglass of Courage
description:
A fairy that

controls the

feelings of others,

instilling them

with bravery.

name: Marine Beast
description:
A sea creature

with sharp teeth

that won't release

a victim once

they're locked on.

name: Warrior of Tradition
description:
A lady warrior

drenched in the 

essence from

a thousand

battlefields.

name: Rock Spirit
description:
A clay idol

representing a rock

spirit. The creature

has significant

attack and defense

factors.

name: Snakeyashi
description:
A creature made up

of several snakes

that attack

separately in battle.

name: Succubus Knight
description:
A vile

warrior wizard

adept at casting

doom-dealing spells.

name: Ill Witch
description:
Controls air

currents and

can generate

a sudden gust

of wind to blow

away an opponent.

name: The Thing That Hides in the Mud
description:
The appearance

of this creature

is preceded by the

ground melting under

an opponent's feet.

name: High Tide Gyojin
description:
An amphibian warrior

that can easily

navigate beneath

the waters.

name: Fairy of the Fountain
description:
A fairy dedicated to

protecting fountains

from pollution.

name: Amazon of the Seas
description:
A mermaid sentry

serving the Sea King

and his kingdom.

name: Nekogal #2
description:
This fast creature

can easily elude

enemy attacks and

counter them with

its vicious claws.

name: Witch's Apprentice
description:
An inexperienced

witch who just

started learning

the mystic arts.

name: Armored Rat
description:
A rat

that is protected

by armor-like fur.

name: Ancient Lizard Warrior
description:
A powerful,

prehistoric

lizard warrior.

name: Maiden of the Moonlight
description:
A lunar sorcerer

that uses mystical

spells to induce

hallucinations.

name: Stone Ogre Grotto
description:
A rock giant

consisting of

massive boulders.

name: Winged Egg of New Life
description:
A messenger of

newborn life.

name: Night Lizard
description:
A green-scaled

lizard warrior

dedicated to 

protecting the sea.

name: Queen's Double
description:
Not very useful

double of a queen.

name: Blue-winged Crown
description:
A bird that glows

with blue flames and

has a head of hair

shaped like a crown.

name: Trent
description:
A protector

of the forest,

this massive tree

continues to grow.

name: Queen of Autumn Leaves
description:
Queen of the

Tree Spirit

who is embraced

by brilliant

autumn leaves.

name: Amphibious Bugroth
description:
A Bugroth unit

modified for

underwater warfare.

name: Acid Crawler
description:
A gigantic

caterpillar that

spits acid capable

of melting

almost anything.

name: Invader of the Throne
description:
A scheming queen

who covets

the king's throne

during his absence.

name: Mystical Sheep #1
description:
A black-haired sheep

that is capable

of sorcery.

name: Disk Magician
description:
A creature that

hides in a saucer

and appears only to

attack enemies.

name: Flame Viper
description:
A very swift,

fire-breathing viper.

name: Royal Guard
description:
Mechanical soldier

with a mind

of its own.

Originally created

to protect members

of the royal family.

name: Gruesome Goo
description:
Looks like any other

slime,

but definitely

much more powerful!

name: Hyosube
description:
This amphibian

creature boasts

a high attack factor,

but not much of one

for defense.

name: Machine Attacker
description:
A machine designed

to blitz its enemies.

name: Hibikime
description:
Confuses enemy

monsters with noise

that is harsh

to the ears.

name: Whiptail Crow
description:
Attacks from the

skies with

a whip-like tail.

name: Kunai with Chain
description:
A boomerang

featuring the

effects of two

cards: the Legendary

Sword and the Sword

of Dark Destruction.

name: Magical Labyrinth
description:
A card for boosting

the power of the

Labyrinth Wall.

name: Warrior Elimination
description:
Destroys all

opponent Warrior

cards played

on the field.

name: Salamandra
description:
Increases the

strength of those

who control the

power of Salamandra.

name: Cursebreaker
description:
Cancels the magic

over all 

level-reduced

monsters and sets

them at level 0.

name: Eternal Rest
description:
Eliminates all

Zombie creatures.

name: Megamorph
description:
A card that

increases the power

of any selected

monster by 2 levels.

name: Metalmorph
description:
A card that changes

any selected monster

to a Machine monster.

name: Winged Trumpeter
description:
A horn that

increases the power

of Fairy creatures.

name: Stain Storm
description:
Acid rain destroys

an opponent's

Machine monsters.

name: Crush Card
description:
Opponent monsters

in play with attack

factors of 1500 or

more are eliminated.

name: Eradicating Aerosol
description:
An insecticide for

wiping out an

opponent's Insect

monsters that are

currently in play.

name: Breath of Light
description:
A magic wind that

reduces to rubble an

opponent's Rock

monsters that are

currently in play.

name: Eternal Draught
description:
A blast of heat

dries up

and eliminates
